WEBVTT

00:12:29.395 --> 00:12:31.478
Bastano i romanzi per addomesticarla,

00:12:31.478 --> 00:12:33.356
invitarla a tavola.

00:12:33.356 --> 00:12:35.229
E guardate chi riunisce:

00:12:35.229 --> 00:12:39.065
il dolce Lestrade, il terrificante Tom Ripley,

00:12:39.065 --> 00:12:43.534
il folle Swann, Marcel Proust stesso.

00:12:43.534 --> 00:12:45.948
Siamo in ottima compagnia.

00:12:45.948 --> 00:12:47.368
Grazie.

00:12:47.368 --> 00:12:52.184
(Applausi)